600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847830/extras/4b123441712445b7350846d83f128549.webm?t=1688307047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847830/extras/4b123441712445b7350846d83f128549.mp4?t=1688307047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is no enemy, you can't lose in this game, so feel free to take your time and explore this soothing world at your own pace.<br>The game lifetime is from 5 to 10 hours, depending if you are more a rusher or an explorer.<br><br><br>If you want to contact us, you can send an email at :<br><a href=\"mailto:spyralfantasy@gmail.com\">spyralfantasy@gmail.com</a><br><br>If you need help or have seen a bug, you can send an email at :<br><a href=\"mailto:spyralfantasy.help@gmail.com\">spyralfantasy.help@gmail.com</a>",
